  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Naturalistic, multicentre, epidemiological study to evaluate the care services used during
      the process of diagnosis of any kind of epilepsy. Data about services since first seizure
      until confirmed diagnosis will be examined.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
